snippet.title: why is everyone dressing as BEANS in Roblox?!
snippet.description:
JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/@GforGaming

HEY EVERYBODY!! 

Niko shows us how to get the free Green Bean costume in Grow A Garden on Roblox! We don't know what the cause is or why it's a thing but... here you go! 
Join The Bean Cause today!!
